  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baf \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u00a0 9126 \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd, \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd, \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "9126 police, army and civil defense personnel are on duty in tomorrow's demonstration",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tomorrow, a massive demonstration will be held against the government including Prime Minister Ranil demanding the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa, and 9126 security forces have been engaged in the related work.",
        "9126 police, army and civil defense officials have been deployed.",
        "These matters have been revealed through a document sent by the Inspector General of Police to the Colombo Deputy Inspector General of Police.",
        "6296 policemen, 1830 soldiers and 1000 civil defense personnel will be deployed.",
        "They will be deployed in two groups with 12-hour duty working hours.",
        "It is to be noted that 6296 police officers engaged in duty include 8 Deputy Inspector Generals of Police, 24 Senior Superintendents of Police, 86 Assistant Superintendents of Police, 392 Principal Police Inspectors, Police Inspectors, Sub Police Inspectors, 5582 Police Constables and 200 Female Police Constables."
      ],
